{"tid":2420003,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「卬度神童又中」股災加核電站爆","createTime":"2021-02-23T15:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T17:41:14.000Z","uid":125460,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"dc14d6c1eba7acceea33627a12061c93e1a4f239","tid":2420003,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"台山核電站機組現故障　反應堆自動停運<br />\n<br />\n廣東省核應急委員會辦公室周二（23日）通報，台山核電站1號機組周日（21日）因配電盤故障，導致核電站1號機組一台主泵停運，機組保護系統實時響應並自動在安全狀況下停止反應堆運作。<br />\n通報指，工作人員得悉狀況後，立即按程序進行故障處理，同時報告核安全監管單位。上述情況處理過程中，機組始終處於安全可控狀態。<br />\n根據國際核事件分級表以及核安全法規，本次問題被界定為0級偏差，強調對機組安全運行、員工健康、周邊公眾和環境並沒有影響。當局事後向香港保安局及澳門警察總局通報事件。"},{"pid":"bcccefc4b10117700809b01168ea5d6e60855034","tid":2420003,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4U7szZ4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4U7szZ4.gif&h=9a52121a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4e3e95a1e2ed79fb424fb9d897a886c7c5d9b61","tid":2420003,"uid":297997,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><strong>強調對</strong></span></strong>機組安全運行、員工健康、<strong><span class=\"red\">周邊公眾和環境並沒有影響</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ae41a466665b86b35662bb02ea7ce8331c4d1c","tid":2420003,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"唔好爆埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d6a1f79fbd7275af4d94e8ace54d92fbfe6b03","tid":2420003,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e4e3e95a1e2ed79fb424fb9d897a886c7c5d9b61","tid":2420003,"uid":297997,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><strong>強調對</strong></span></strong>機組安全運行、員工健康、<strong><span class=\"red\">周邊公眾和環境並沒有影響</span></strong><img sr